column1:
Directions: Please enter the contact information of all employers your program has provided a service to from July 1, 2017 to June 30, 2018 (i.e. workplace classes, corrections, WAGE, etc). Please insert a row for each location even if it is the same employer. Please DO NOT include more than one employer contact  information in a single cell. 
If you did not serve any employers during the 2017-18 program year, please type N/A in Column B.
If the type of service is not listed in the drop down box, please make comments in Column H.
